Sangria — Recursive Folding Engine — License & Provenance
=========================================================

SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT

Copyright (c) 2025-2026 The Soqucoin Core developers

Original work by Soqucoin: a clean-room implementation of a Sangria-style
recursive folding engine providing constant-size Dilithium batch verification
(built on the Binius commitment scheme in `src/crypto/binius/`). Licensed under
the MIT License; the full license text is in the repository root `COPYING`.

This module implements a published cryptographic construction; it is not derived
from third-party source code.
